{"id":46419,"date":"2025-12-23T21:39:41","date_gmt":"2025-12-23T18:39:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/e-museum.kz\/exhibit\/68da7efa4ec055fcb-en\/"},"modified":"2025-12-31T12:51:35","modified_gmt":"2025-12-31T09:51:35","slug":"68da7efa4ec055fcb-en","status":"publish","type":"exhibit","link":"https:\/\/e-museum.kz\/en\/exhibit\/68da7efa4ec055fcb-en\/","title":{"rendered":"Medal &#171;60 years of the USSR Armed Forces&#187;"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>The obverse of the medal features an image of a Soviet Army soldier with a submachine gun against a background of sky-high missiles and flying combat aircraft. To the right of the soldier&#8217;s figure, a submarine is depicted on the sea horizon, above which the dates &#171;1918&#187; and &#171;1978&#187; are arranged in two lines. On the reverse side of the medal, the inscriptions are placed around the circumference: &#171;Sixty years&#187; and &#171;Armed Forces of the USSR&#187;, separated by asterisks. In the center is an image of a five\u2014pointed star with a hammer and a plow in the middle, superimposed on a crossed rifle and a saber. The edges of the medal are bordered by a rim. All inscriptions and images on the medal are convex. The medal is connected by means of an eyelet and a ring to a pentagonal shoe covered with a 24 mm wide gray silk moire ribbon. The edges of the ribbon are edged with a 5 mm wide red stripe. In the middle of the ribbon is a longitudinal strip of golden color with a width of 1 mm.<br \/>\nDimensions: diameter &#8212; 3 cm, height with pad \u2013 8.5 cm.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":0,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"default","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site